[35m│[0m sanitization. Both semicolon-based injection and backtick injection were     [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m tested. Semicolon injection works perfectly and leaks command output into    [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m the JSON response message. The payload structure `url=http://example.com";   [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m <command> #` successfully executes arbitrary commands. Key findings:         [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m                                                                              [35m│[0m
