[35m│[0m                                                                              [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m The URL validation mechanism does not exist - any string including shell     [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m metacharacters is passed to an OS command that checks URL status. The        [35m│[0m
[35m│[0m command execution is synchronous and output is reflected in the response.    [35m│[0m
